 <img src=\"/assets/images/services/rehab-nursing.webp\" width=\"640\" height=\"363\" alt=\"Rehabilitation Facility Environmental Cleaning in Agawam, MA\" class=\"card__image\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n </div>\n <div class=\"card__body\">\n <h3 class=\"card__title\">Rehabilitation & Nursing Facilities</h3>\n <p class=\"card__text\">Comprehensive cleaning for rehabilitation centers, nursing facilities, and long-term care environments.</p>\n <a href=\"/services/rehab-nursing/agawam-ma\" class=\"btn btn--primary\">Learn More</a>\n </div>\n </article>\n <article class=\"card service-card\">\n <div class=\"card__image-wrapper\">\n <img src=\"/assets/images/services/healthcare-admin.webp\" width=\"424\" height=\"241\" alt=\"Healthcare Admin Office Environmental Cleaning in Agawam, MA\" class=\"card__image\" loading=\"lazy\" decoding=\"async\">\n </div>\n <div class=\"card__body\">\n <h3 class=\"card__title\">Healthcare Admin Offices</h3>\n <p class=\"card__text\">Professional cleaning for healthcare administrative offices, medical billing centers, and health system headquarters.</p>\n <a href=\"/services/healthcare-admin-offices/agawam-ma\" class=\"btn btn--primary\">Learn More</a>\n </div>\n </article>\n </div>\n </div>\n </section>\n\n \n        <!-- Why Choose Us in [City] -->\n        <section class=\"section why-choose-section\" style=\"background:#f8fafc;\">\n          <div class=\"container container--narrow\">\n            <h2 class=\"section__title\" style=\"margin-bottom:1.5rem;\">Why Agawam Healthcare Facilities Trust Dory's Cleaning</h2>\n            <p style=\"font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.75;color:#475569;margin-bottom:1.5rem;\">Healthcare facilities in Agawam, Hampden County, face stringent infection control standards required by the Massachusetts Department of Public Health, OSHA, CDC, and EPA. Dory's Cleaning Services brings 22+ years of clinical healthcare experience to every Agawam medical office, clinic, nursing facility, and healthcare administrative space we serve.</p>\n            <p style=\"font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.75;color:#475569;margin-bottom:1.5rem;\">Unlike standard janitorial companies, our team is specifically trained in bloodborne pathogen handling, EPA-registered hospital-grade disinfectant application, terminal cleaning protocols, and HIPAA-aware environmental services. We understand the difference between visual cleanliness and verifiable disinfection — and we deliver written documentation to support your facility's compliance program.</p>\n\n            <h3 style=\"font-size:1.4rem;margin:2rem 0 1rem;color:#1e293b;\">Healthcare Facilities We Clean in Agawam</h3>\n            <ul style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;margin-bottom:2rem;\">\n              <li style=\"padding:0.625rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;color:#475569;\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"vertical-align:-4px;margin-right:0.5rem;\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"12\" r=\"9\"/><path d=\"M12 8v8M8 12h8\"/></svg><strong>Medical offices &amp; physician practices</strong> — internal medicine, family medicine, OB/GYN, pediatrics</li>\n              <li style=\"padding:0.625rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;color:#475569;\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"vertical-align:-4px;margin-right:0.5rem;\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M9 3h6v6l4 4v8H5v-8l4-4z\"/><path d=\"M9 3v6M15 3v6\"/></svg><strong>Specialty clinics</strong> — cardiology, dermatology, dental, urgent care, orthopedics</li>\n              <li style=\"padding:0.625rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;color:#475569;\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"vertical-align:-4px;margin-right:0.5rem;\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><circle cx=\"12\" cy=\"5\" r=\"1.5\"/><path d=\"M9 22l3-8 3 4M9 14l-2-4 3-3 4 3-1 4M5 13l3-4\"/></svg><strong>Ambulatory &amp; outpatient centers</strong> — same-day surgery, infusion centers, dialysis</li>\n              <li style=\"padding:0.625rem 0;border-bottom:1px solid #e2e8f0;color:#475569;\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"vertical-align:-4px;margin-right:0.5rem;\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><path d=\"M10.5 4.5l9 9a4.95 4.95 0 0 1-7 7l-9-9a4.95 4.95 0 0 1 7-7z\"/><path d=\"M8.5 8.5l7 7\"/></svg><strong>Rehab &amp; nursing facilities</strong> — long-term care, skilled nursing, memory care</li>\n              <li style=\"padding:0.625rem 0;color:#475569;\"><svg width=\"20\" height=\"20\" viewBox=\"0 0 24 24\" fill=\"none\" stroke=\"currentColor\" stroke-width=\"1.75\" stroke-linecap=\"round\" stroke-linejoin=\"round\" style=\"vertical-align:-4px;margin-right:0.5rem;\" role=\"img\" focusable=\"false\" aria-hidden=\"true\"><rect x=\"8\" y=\"2\" width=\"8\" height=\"4\" rx=\"1\"/><path d=\"M16 4h2a2 2 0 0 1 2 2v14a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H6a2 2 0 0 1-2-2V6a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h2\"/><path d=\"M9 13l2 2 4-4\"/></svg><strong>Healthcare admin offices</strong> — billing centers, medical records, hospital headquarters</li>\n            </ul>\n\n            <h3 style=\"font-size:1.4rem;margin:2rem 0 1rem;color:#1e293b;\">What's Included in Agawam Healthcare Cleaning</h3>\n            <p style=\"font-size:1.0625rem;line-height:1.75;color:#475569;margin-bottom:1rem;\">Every cleaning visit to your Agawam facility includes:</p>\n            <ul style=\"list-style:none;padding:0;margin-bottom:2rem;\">\n              <li style=\"paddi